Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.93,0:00:13.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟是谁…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.95,0:00:17.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非是…他？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.10,0:02:04.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公元2307年
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.60,0:02:07.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自Celestial Being开始武力干预以来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.96,0:02:10.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,4个月的时间即将过去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.25,0:02:14.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们的干预行动超过了60次
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.75,0:02:20.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管人们是否愿意  都在逐渐接受他们的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.95,0:02:24.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论是Celestial Being的反对者还是支持者
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.86,0:02:29.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在反对战争方面都是一致的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.03,0:02:32.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁都不希望有战争
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.34,0:02:36.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在地球上的三个国家群中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.24,0:02:41.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,联合和AEU仅在同盟国内的纷争事变方面
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.14,0:02:46.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发表了针对Celestial Being的防御行动
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.14,0:02:52.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但自从莫拉里亚纷争以来却未曾出现过一次大规模的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.58,0:02:58.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之所以会有这种事  是因为MS Gundam的卓越战斗能力
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.92,0:03:03.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界范围内出现的纷争在不断缩小
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.15,0:03:07.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但对于武力压制的反对却并未消失
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.51,0:03:14.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在  在唯一以对决姿态面对他们的人类革新联盟中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.63,0:03:17.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,某个极秘作战计划即将展开
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.41,0:03:23.43,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(500,500)}#09  大国的威信
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.42,0:03:21.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特务部队  顶武队员的各位
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.54,0:03:27.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位既是本国的代表  也是人类革新联盟的精英
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.43,0:03:28.99,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(500,500)}人革联  高轨道平台
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.94,0:03:32.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位的任务是剿灭在世界范围内持续着武力干预的武装组织
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.13,0:03:35.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并夺取MS
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.11,0:03:37.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若能完成这一任务
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.16,0:03:40.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我们人类革新联盟将引领世界
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.32,0:03:44.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并对人类的发展作出巨大贡献
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.90,0:03:47.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,期望各位抖擞精神
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.22,0:03:53.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dynames  着舰完成
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.14,0:03:56.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下面进入Exia的着舰作业
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.65,0:04:00.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,运输器打开  相对诱导系统启动
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.24,0:04:05.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诱导系统  同步
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.15,0:04:07.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Exia  现在着舰
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.14,0:04:17.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Exia  着舰完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.90,0:04:28.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,着舰得不错哦  刹那
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.37,0:04:30.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我帮忙进行整备
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.84,0:04:34.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回房间休息去吧  别抢别人的饭碗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.01,0:04:38.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥  哥哥  大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.71,0:04:40.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是感动的会面啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.83,0:04:44.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始整备  开始整备
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.80,0:04:46.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白  明白
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.91,0:04:47.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.58,0:04:53.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皇小姐  若在大修中遇上敌袭该如何是好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.72,0:04:54.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怨老天吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.68,0:04:58.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这算是战术预报员的话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.98,0:05:17.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姿态控制完成  舱门打开
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.39,0:05:20.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,线性弹射器电压上升
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.83,0:05:23.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,双向通信系统  发射准备完成
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.61,0:05:25.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发射
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.08,0:05:29.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通信子机  整体分离
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.96,0:05:40.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通信子机开始整体分离  正在向预定位置移动
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.65,0:05:41.05,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(0,0)}人革联  高轨道平台管制室
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.97,0:05:43.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,双向通信正常
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.74,0:05:48.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样一来  我军的静止卫星轨道区域已覆盖了80%
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.01,0:05:49.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.57,0:05:52.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam放射出的特殊粒子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.75,0:05:56.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,具有干扰效果范围内的通信设备的特性
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.89,0:05:58.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反其道而行之
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.55,0:06:02.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通过进行双向通信  释放出几十万的小型探测装置
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.13,0:06:04.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,则在有无法通信的区域时
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.05,0:06:07.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是表明有Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.04,0:06:11.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中校  鱼儿会上钩吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.84,0:06:14.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若不是这样可就不好办了  明副官
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.21,0:06:18.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,投入如此大量物资的作战计划并非随便要进行几次都可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.73,0:06:22.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在Celestial Being的动向下的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.28,0:06:24.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界纷争今后的状况…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.69,0:06:26.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是麻烦的论文啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.74,0:06:28.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种东西  随便写写不就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.97,0:06:30.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样子可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.25,0:06:31.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路易丝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.63,0:06:33.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈…妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.40,0:06:35.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.19,0:06:40.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想见你啊  路易丝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.83,0:06:43.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在不是在航行管制吗  为什么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.23,0:06:46.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了代议员老师
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.11,0:06:49.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路易丝  这位是？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.45,0:06:53.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次和你提起过吧  我的男友
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.79,0:06:56.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫沙慈  沙慈·克洛斯罗德
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.44,0:06:59.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  女儿给你添麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.55,0:07:00.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.21,0:07:02.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  也该够了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.37,0:07:05.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  回去吧  路易丝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.75,0:07:07.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么呢  妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.34,0:07:09.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界现在这种状况
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.48,0:07:12.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么能让女孩子家一个人在外留学呢  好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.70,0:07:13.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要嘛  我不回去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.07,0:07:15.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说点什么啊  沙慈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.11,0:07:17.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是这么说…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.84,0:07:19.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恋人要被带走了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.12,0:07:20.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恋人？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.27,0:07:22.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什么时候
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.54,0:07:23.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.78,0:07:25.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您…您误会了  妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.58,0:07:26.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.54,0:07:28.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不是  我不是这意思…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.16,0:07:30.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是男孩子的话就干脆点
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.22,0:07:31.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.16,0:07:33.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙慈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.20,0:07:37.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对伊奥利亚·修亨伯格的调查报道？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.87,0:07:40.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若对Celestial Being的创始人进行调查
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.43,0:07:42.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那应该就能知道他们的真正目的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.48,0:07:44.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请一定让我来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.46,0:07:49.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说无论哪个国家的谍报机关都毫无办法
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.44,0:07:50.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一个人能怎么…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.86,0:07:53.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便如此我也想做  拜托你了  主任
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.63,0:08:00.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能在1月内收集到1分钟的报道特辑题材吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.28,0:08:02.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.63,0:08:03.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一则新闻
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.93,0:08:10.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx95}联合国对能量枯竭状况日益加剧的中东王国阿扎提斯坦进行了援助
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.74,0:08:15.20,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(500,500)}阿扎提斯坦王国\N阿扎提斯坦王国国际机场
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.39,0:08:14.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,联合国的视察团已经抵达当地…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.62,0:08:21.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若能和联合国大使谈得拢  那太阳光发电系统也会对本国…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.41,0:08:23.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主  好像到了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.42,0:08:31.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这位会拯救阿扎提斯坦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.69,0:08:35.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次见面
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.86,0:08:38.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是联合国大使  亚历桑德罗·柯纳
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.96,0:08:42.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是阿扎提斯坦王国第一公主  玛丽娜·伊斯迈尔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.40,0:08:45.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能接受我们的援助请求
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.86,0:08:48.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我谨代表我国表示谢意
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.82,0:08:52.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,联合国原本就是为此而成立的组织
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.05,0:08:59.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话虽如此  如今加盟国滞纳分担费用  能办到的事十分有限
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.66,0:09:01.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便如此  还是要谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.54,0:09:04.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,联合国在这种时候的援助
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.43,0:09:07.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明没什么东西能够抵押
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.07,0:09:10.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个男的  在想些什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.79,0:09:17.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  菲露特呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.65,0:09:20.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是身体不适  到莫雷诺那边去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.96,0:09:22.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是指值班人连小姐吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.58,0:09:23.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.28,0:09:27.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边交给我  你去吃饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.33,0:09:29.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  真的吗  好体贴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.82,0:09:30.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.20,0:09:33.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  不是我喜欢的类型
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.72,0:09:36.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可悲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.68,0:09:42.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟  在干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.65,0:09:43.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛克恩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.95,0:09:48.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.14,0:10:03.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不太融洽…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.46,0:10:08.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GN驱动器填充  到达100%
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.49,0:10:17.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AE3288的双向通信中断了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.61,0:10:18.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向中校汇报
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.04,0:10:20.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AR9763也是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.03,0:10:22.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,位置是EAN07
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.90,0:10:25.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到会是这么近…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.55,0:10:27.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向特务部队  顶武的全体成员传达
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.23,0:10:30.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MS队  紧急出发
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.61,0:10:31.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紧急出击准备
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.60,0:10:36.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(500,500)}人革联  多用途运输舰  拉奥和
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.20,0:10:35.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自0655  从1号舰起依次出击
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.59,0:10:39.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全搭乘人员加速准备
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.48,0:10:42.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在140秒后开始紧急加速
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.61,0:10:48.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佩丽丝少尉  全感觉投影系统状况如何
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.28,0:10:54.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有问题  中校  一切正常
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.41,0:10:57.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这对少尉而言可是首次实战
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.38,0:10:59.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可不希望发生上次那种事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.02,0:11:01.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白  中校
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.99,0:11:04.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全舰达到可加速区域
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.56,0:11:05.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加速开始
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.88,0:11:12.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  菲露特的父母曾在Celestial Being待过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.36,0:11:15.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说两人都是第二代的Gundam Meister
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.64,0:11:16.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.41,0:11:20.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是托你父母的福才战斗的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.66,0:11:24.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你是想家了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.72,0:11:27.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是两人的祭日
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.67,0:11:28.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出了什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.07,0:11:31.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道  只知道是过世了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.38,0:11:35.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Celestial Being的成员有保密的义务
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.96,0:11:38.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不清楚当前成员的过去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.68,0:11:42.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊  连双亲的消息也…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.79,0:11:46.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你继承了双亲的遗志呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.35,0:11:51.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很坚强  是个坚强的女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.46,0:11:59.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尼尔  我原名叫尼尔·迪兰地
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.44,0:12:00.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的名字？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.81,0:12:02.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  没错
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.40,0:12:06.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出身于爱尔兰  双亲死于恐怖袭击
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.65,0:12:09.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.40,0:12:13.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老是由你说  不太公平吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.01,0:12:15.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好体贴
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.35,0:12:16.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仅限于对女性吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.22,0:12:17.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛克恩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.80,0:12:19.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打…打搅了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.97,0:12:20.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别误会
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.88,0:12:22.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.87,0:12:25.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  那种状况下  能尝出什么味道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.87,0:12:26.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.89,0:12:27.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.62,0:12:29.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.92,0:12:31.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,E传感器有反应
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.40,0:12:34.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…通信装置
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.08,0:12:35.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.98,0:12:36.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.64,0:12:37.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.40,0:12:39.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人探测到了我们的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.85,0:12:45.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,改变托勒密的轨道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.39,0:12:47.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以最短距离朝轨道环前进
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.51,0:12:48.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.80,0:12:50.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各Meister在Gundam待机
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.05,0:12:52.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊恩  Gundam的整备状况呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.32,0:12:57.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Exia整备好了  但Dynames的脚部发电机还无法使用
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.94,0:12:59.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,装甲也处于拆除状态
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.38,0:13:01.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要的机体…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.70,0:13:04.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让Kyrios  Virtue先出击
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.75,0:13:05.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.39,0:13:05.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲露特
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.56,0:13:07.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要活下来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.02,0:13:08.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.36,0:13:11.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托勒密  转为弹射模式
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.08,0:13:18.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然通过散布几十万的通信装置来确定GN粒子的通信遮断区域
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.09,0:13:22.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能采用这种大量物资作战计划的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.65,0:13:23.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕是人革…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.14,0:13:25.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,状况如何
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.07,0:13:28.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很糟  无法突破敌方通信区域
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.23,0:13:31.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝轨道环的发电卫星前进
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.75,0:13:34.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由于电磁波的影响  那里为无通信地带
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.47,0:13:37.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若状况能维持5分钟的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.44,0:13:38.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.46,0:13:39.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kyrios已出击
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.38,0:13:42.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使Virtue转移至弹射甲板
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.37,0:13:45.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想以两台Gundam进行佯攻吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.51,0:13:46.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然也有此意…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.29,0:13:48.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.94,0:13:50.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲露特  出击顺序拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.19,0:13:51.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.92,0:13:56.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通过应急处理在左脚上装上了固定用具
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.83,0:13:58.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但武器管制的调节…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.29,0:13:59.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能射击就行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.31,0:13:59.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.15,0:14:03.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油  加油
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.26,0:14:06.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Virtue  特瑞亚·埃德  出击
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.84,0:14:16.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中校  朝轨道环前进的通信遮断点又增加了两处
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.09,0:14:19.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam分散了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.85,0:14:23.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  这是让两台Gundam出击的佯攻
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.68,0:14:26.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若是这样  那处于第一通信遮断点的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.89,0:14:30.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很可能就是Celestial Being的宇宙运输舰
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.65,0:14:34.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  就以牙还牙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.65,0:14:38.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1号舰到3号舰  MS全体出击
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.30,0:14:42.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2号  3号的掌舵员  切换成自动掌舵
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.55,0:14:44.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在舰桥分离后  返回基地
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.70,0:14:49.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3号舰  别忘了跟踪第3通信遮断点
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.59,0:14:54.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1号舰到3号舰  MS全体出击
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.05,0:14:58.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按照预定  在1号舰后方形成纵列队形
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.23,0:15:01.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2号、3号舰  舰桥脱离
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.18,0:15:05.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3号舰  开始跟踪第3通信遮断点
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.89,0:15:08.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2号舰  跟踪第2通信遮断点
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.86,0:15:09.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进入轨道变更
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.47,0:15:14.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本队以1号舰为主轴  追踪第1通信遮断点
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.45,0:15:17.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目标推测是敌运输舰
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.40,0:15:20.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要能捕捉到  进入作战行动
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.05,0:15:24.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托勒密  已进入轨道环的电磁波干涉区域
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.77,0:15:26.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光学摄像机捕捉到敌方部队
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.20,0:15:27.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.52,0:15:30.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最大望远距离  在显示屏上显示
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.46,0:15:33.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靠近的舰船
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.97,0:15:38.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是人类革新联盟军的多用途运输舰EDI402拉奥和
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.73,0:15:39.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,断定有四艘
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.26,0:15:42.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两艘分别在左右散开了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.90,0:15:45.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,估计是去攻击Kyrios和Virtue
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.34,0:15:47.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中招了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.10,0:15:49.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向阿里路亚他们的通信呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.01,0:15:52.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,处于电磁波干涉区域  这不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.84,0:15:54.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里希特  马上改变轨道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.20,0:15:58.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以轨道环作为掩护  与敌舰保持距离
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.45,0:15:59.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明  明白
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.20,0:16:05.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌舰改变轨道  隐藏到了轨道环的阴影中
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.85,0:16:07.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有两下子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.61,0:16:09.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能显示敌舰的舰影吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.91,0:16:11.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利用AI进行过了修正
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.77,0:16:13.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系  显示
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.75,0:16:17.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是Celestial Being的宇宙船
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.39,0:16:23.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说那个组织的规模大到连这种东西都有吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.57,0:16:29.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向全体成员传达战术分析员的状况预测
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.66,0:16:32.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靠近的舰船有两艘运输舰——拉奥和
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.67,0:16:36.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,估计敌方所有的战力都集中在了那里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.27,0:16:37.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.70,0:16:41.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两艘敌舰应该去迎击Kyrios和Virtue了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.69,0:16:43.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来不希望那样的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.62,0:16:45.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来的计划
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.92,0:16:48.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是希望看穿我们佯攻的敌方舰队会忽略阿里路亚他们
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.06,0:16:50.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而直接朝我们过来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.08,0:16:55.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是那样  那就能像预定那样绕到敌军后方来进行夹击了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.68,0:16:58.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人以佯攻来应对我们的佯攻
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.35,0:17:04.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前去攻击的敌方运输舰上所搭载的MS恐怕已全部出击
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.51,0:17:09.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相反  \N阿里路亚和特瑞亚估计正在迎击运输舰  从而耗费了时间
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.37,0:17:15.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真费工夫
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.09,0:17:19.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有搭载MS？  不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.92,0:17:22.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遭遇敌人佯攻的阿里路亚他们
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.01,0:17:24.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我估计会在6分钟后回来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.00,0:17:28.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其间  我们将受到敌方MS部队的波浪式进攻
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.43,0:17:31.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皇小姐  你这么预测的根据是？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.88,0:17:37.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,18年前  在第4次太阳光纷争时采用了与此相同的作战计划
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.73,0:17:39.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人革联的作战指挥官
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.62,0:17:43.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是俄罗斯的外号叫作「暴熊」的谢尔盖·斯密尔诺夫
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.08,0:17:45.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是本队的作战开始时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.42,0:17:48.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可不要浪费生命
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.09,0:17:52.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Exia  Dynames  运输器舱门打开
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.40,0:17:56.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Exia在普特利麦奥斯的前方以迎击形态待机
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.27,0:18:07.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dynames  将脚部固定在运输器上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.60,0:18:11.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用GN来复枪以迎击射击状态待机
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.48,0:18:16.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将托勒密的优先权转为防御
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.34,0:18:18.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切断常规电源
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.41,0:18:21.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真…真的要开战吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.10,0:18:24.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这艘船明明没有武器
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.35,0:18:25.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有Gundam在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.22,0:18:27.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不只有两台吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.10,0:18:29.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  敌方该出击了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.85,0:18:31.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坚持360秒试试
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.21,0:18:34.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌方运输舰从环的阴影中出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.51,0:18:36.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dynames  开始炮击阻击战
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.49,0:18:37.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.65,0:18:41.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由于机体重量的变化  瞄准偏了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.15,0:18:43.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈罗修正  哈罗修正
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.06,0:18:45.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没时间了  用手动了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.55,0:18:49.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有导弹靠近  数量为24
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.94,0:18:50.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狙击
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.68,0:18:57.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.43,0:18:58.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GN场展开
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.78,0:18:59.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明  明白
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.25,0:19:06.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种速度
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.51,0:19:09.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是用无人舰采取的特攻
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.49,0:19:10.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特  特攻…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.18,0:19:11.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.27,0:19:13.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.35,0:19:14.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会让你们得逞吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.62,0:19:25.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GN场再次展开
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.37,0:19:27.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.98,0:19:28.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克里斯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.99,0:19:34.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快来  阿里路亚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.70,0:19:36.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想死…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.22,0:19:38.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克里斯蒂娜·西尔纳
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.59,0:19:39.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要活下来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.32,0:19:46.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全员…要活下来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.36,0:19:48.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲露特
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.73,0:19:53.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲露特说得没错  我们要活下来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.78,0:19:55.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管如何  都要坚持下来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.95,0:19:57.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已确认敌方MS部队
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.27,0:20:03.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,躲在了运输舰的后方吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.00,0:20:05.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌方总数为36台
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.91,0:20:06.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虚张声势
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.34,0:20:13.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进入了死角
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.95,0:20:15.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰桥  转一下运输器
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.43,0:20:25.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在引诱我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.70,0:20:33.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果上前  那防御便会变得薄弱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.05,0:20:36.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捕捉到了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.95,0:20:37.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.03,0:20:39.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌方姿态不确定
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.82,0:20:42.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若是这种程度的攻击的话  那可以用GN场来应付
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.68,0:20:44.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克里斯蒂娜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.66,0:20:45.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道  菲露特
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.27,0:20:48.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再稍微  稍微…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.89,0:20:52.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有悖MS的舰船攻击理论的远距离攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.10,0:20:56.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是这么回事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.18,0:20:57.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人革联
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.24,0:21:02.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  谢尔盖·斯密尔诺夫此次的作战目的并不是托勒密
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.52,0:21:03.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是捕获Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.95,0:21:07.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是说我的预测失算了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.41,0:21:09.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.92,0:21:12.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明决定不会再搞错了的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.36,0:21:18.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捕捉到了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.55,0:21:20.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  怎么了  这是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.45,0:21:25.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机械雷部队  被诱导了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.90,0:21:37.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才这种程度  Kyrios会…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.13,0:21:42.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事  这种像刺中了头部一样的疼痛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.29,0:21:45.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一…一样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.79,0:21:48.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和那时一样的疼痛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.24,0:21:52.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是什么  到底是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.72,0:21:54.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那台机体是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.72,0:21:56.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认识
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.95,0:22:01.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认识你！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.81,0:22:16.58,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}絶望は甘い罠
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.49,0:22:21.23,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}鎖されたその扉
